This is the source code for the Ada-DK Wiki The Dice Roller tutorial program.

It is not intended to be a full-fledged diceroller, but merely a demonstration
on how one such could be done in Ada.

Full instructions on usage can be found at this URL:

    http://wiki.ada-dk.org/index.php/The_Dice_Roller_Program

This program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful, but WITHOUT 
ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS
FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.
